{"tid":1897380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎喺日韓爆發係connect港日韓三地人民嘅機會","createTime":"2020-02-25T16:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T02:49:28.000Z","uid":27764,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7886e91541b69c7b1e2b976268d14cfee00b03d8","tid":1897380,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"記唔記得日本311地震嘅時候，台灣人對日本嘅捐款數目係世界第一? <br />\n日本人一直都無忘記台灣人嘅幫助，今年東京奧運好多城市都爭住做台灣國家隊嘅接待城市<br />\n<br />\n而家日本同韓國都受武漢肺炎所害，香港人雖然提供唔到咩實質幫助，但係都可以精神上支持下佢地，而唔係踩佢地抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如周庭大J呢啲精通日語嘅可以拍片為日本人打氣，大家應該connect埋佢地，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">突顯香港人同中國人係兩個唔同嘅民族</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeb3a121fff1acd60bb274665c5478c9b891a4f","tid":1897380,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b36a81601986035889e78f3e31a7611036a3fd2f","tid":1897380,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"以香港市民名義拍條南韓加油得唔得?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897076\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897076</a><br />\n話晒南韓咁支持香港"},{"pid":"c49b10c5058497ddf3a3eba24655809ca7483eb3","tid":1897380,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b7348ba1d6707aa858d1ce7fdb1c067e04f813e9","tid":1897380,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}